    {
        "id": "f1",
        "type": "tab",
        "label": "Topic 2 — MQTT All-in-One",
        "disabled": false,
        "info": "Flow Node-RED untuk demo Topik 2 (MQTT All-in-One).\n\n=== KOMPONEN ===\n1. Sensor DHT22 (subscribe bootcamp/sensor/01) → Gauge + Chart\n2. Kontrol Pintu (button → publish UNLOCK ke bootcamp/kontrol/pintu)\n3. Audit Log (subscribe bootcamp/status/pintu → text display)\n\n=== CARA PAKAI ===\n1. Pastikan Wokwi simulation (sketch Topik 2) sudah jalan & MQTT connected.\n2. Deploy flow ini di Node-RED.\n3. Buka http://localhost:1880/ui untuk lihat dashboard.\n4. Klik button 'Buka Pintu' → relay Wokwi aktif 3 detik.\n5. Audit log terupdate real-time: ADMIN_REMOTE → UNLOCKED → LOCKED.\n\n=== TROUBLESHOOTING ===\n- Bila mqtt in node berstatus 'disconnected' → cek internet / broker publik.\n- Bila dashboard blank → install dulu node-red-dashboard: npm i node-red-dashboard.\n- Topic tabrakan dengan peserta lain → ganti prefix 'bootcamp' jadi 'bootcamp/<nama>'."
    },
